  "text": "Small differences in seed PAs at véraison were observed, with only lower seed PAs when day background temperature was cooled [CITATION_1] . However, the effect of cooled days and heated nights was consistent, showing no effects on total PAs but with mDP and EC subunits increased while ECG was reduced in seeds at véraison [CITATION_2] .",
